178
00:11:16,428 --> 00:11:19,927
A la mañana siguiente.

179
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:24,369
- No es Harry.
- Vamos, Con.

180
00:11:24,569 --> 00:11:26,514
Es una pantalla perfecta.

181
00:11:26,714 --> 00:11:30,753
- No es Harry.
- Entonces, ¿quién carajos es?

182
00:11:31,065 --> 00:11:34,605
No es... Harry.

183
00:11:34,805 --> 00:11:38,234
